				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I like this KVC mini-rant from Gus Mueller&#8217;s post about writing &#8220;Acorn plug-ins in JavaScript&#8221;:http://gusmueller.com/blog/archives/2009/01/jscocoa_and_acorn_plugins_in_javascript.html:</p>
