<p>Gus has been posting to both his personal and company blogs lately. Another neat script over on the Flying Meat blog is &#8220;this one about drop shadows&#8221;:http://flyingmeat.com/blog/archives/2009/01/curved_drop_shadows_in_acorn.html.</p>
